Package domain.locations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Exit
    An exit from on room/location to another.
    GameObject
    An object within the game that is interact-able.
    Location
    This is used to group together a series of Rooms, and is only created once in the LocationsController.createLocations().
    LocationsController
    The main controller for the domain.locations package.
    Room
    A room within a location.
